This project – a Youth Art Media Platform/Publication -  will be the first of its kind in the region.
=======
This project will be the first of its kind in the region, working outside of schools but with the as well..
>>>>>>> schools_project

It convenes high school reporters to produce a multi-media arts-journalism publication with the goal of giving them a voice in the metro area and help them become a resource on the arts for the Louisville region. 
 
The project – run by media professionals working with educators – would publish arts-related content of existing high school publication but also create opportunities for young people to cover the arts throughout the Louisville metropolitan area. 
 
That includes weighing in on touring Broadway productions, other theater, music and dance performances as well as art exhibits; profiling artists and arts groups; examining issues related to art and interrelated issues such as public issues such as health, safety, education, the economy and history...
